11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_G711_AUDIO_ENCODER_PCM_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_G711_AUDIO_ENCODER_PCM_H_
13
14#include <utility>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_encoder.h"
19#include "api/units/time_delta.h"
20#include "rtc_base/constructor_magic.h"
21
22namespace webrtc {
23
24class AudioEncoderPcm : public AudioEncoder {
25 public:
26 struct Config {
27 public:
28 bool IsOk() const;
29
30 int frame_size_ms;
31 size_t num_channels;
32 int payload_type;
33
34 protected:
35 explicit Config(int pt)
36 : frame_size_ms(20), num_channels(1), payload_type(pt) {}
37 };
38
39 ~AudioEncoderPcm() override;
40
41 int SampleRateHz() const override;
42 size_t NumChannels() const override;
43 size_t Num10MsFramesInNextPacket() const override;
44 size_t Max10MsFramesInAPacket() const override;
45 int GetTargetBitrate() const override;
46 void Reset() override;
47 absl::optional<std::pair<TimeDelta, TimeDelta>> GetFrameLengthRange()
48 const override;
49
50 protected:
51 AudioEncoderPcm(const Config& config, int sample_rate_hz);
52
53 EncodedInfo EncodeImpl(uint32_t rtp_timestamp,
54 rtc::ArrayView<const int16_t> audio,
55 rtc::Buffer* encoded) override;
56
57 virtual size_t EncodeCall(const int16_t* audio,
58 size_t input_len,
59 uint8_t* encoded) = 0;
60
61 virtual size_t BytesPerSample() const = 0;
62
63 // Used to set EncodedInfoLeaf::encoder_type in
64 // AudioEncoderPcm::EncodeImpl
65 virtual AudioEncoder::CodecType GetCodecType() const = 0;
66
67 private:
68 const int sample_rate_hz_;
69 const size_t num_channels_;
70 const int payload_type_;
71 const size_t num_10ms_frames_per_packet_;
72 const size_t full_frame_samples_;
73 std::vector<int16_t> speech_buffer_;
74 uint32_t first_timestamp_in_buffer_;
75};
76
77class AudioEncoderPcmA final : public AudioEncoderPcm {
78 public:
79 struct Config : public AudioEncoderPcm::Config {
80 Config() : AudioEncoderPcm::Config(8) {}
81 };
82
83 explicit AudioEncoderPcmA(const Config& config)
84 : AudioEncoderPcm(config, kSampleRateHz) {}
85
86 protected:
87 size_t EncodeCall(const int16_t* audio,
88 size_t input_len,
89 uint8_t* encoded) override;
90
91 size_t BytesPerSample() const override;
92
93 AudioEncoder::CodecType GetCodecType() const override;
94
95 private:
96 static const int kSampleRateHz = 8000;
97 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(AudioEncoderPcmA);
98};
99
100class AudioEncoderPcmU final : public AudioEncoderPcm {
101 public:
102 struct Config : public AudioEncoderPcm::Config {
103 Config() : AudioEncoderPcm::Config(0) {}
104 };
105
106 explicit AudioEncoderPcmU(const Config& config)
107 : AudioEncoderPcm(config, kSampleRateHz) {}
108
109 protected:
110 size_t EncodeCall(const int16_t* audio,
111 size_t input_len,
112 uint8_t* encoded) override;
113
114 size_t BytesPerSample() const override;
115
116 AudioEncoder::CodecType GetCodecType() const override;
117
118 private:
119 static const int kSampleRateHz = 8000;
120 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(AudioEncoderPcmU);
121};
122
123} // namespace webrtc
124
125#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_CODECS_G711_AUDIO_ENCODER_PCM_H_
